text: Everything is getting more expensive for Canadians including necessities like groceries and heating your home thanks to Justin Trudeau’s rising taxes and his Carbon Tax. I will bring in #TaxFreeHomeHeating to help Canadians get ahead, not just get by.pic.twitter.com/E4FycmnGxQ

We’re fighting climate change by putting a price on pollution, and giving the money right back to Canadians. Remember to claim your Climate Action Incentive as you file your taxes this year.pic.twitter.com/gAGSrqF47m
